001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007@HistoryLogProps(
008    opCode = 66,
009    displayName = "Bolus Requested 3/3",
010    internalName = "LID_BOLUS_REQUESTED_MSG3",
011    usedByAndroid = true,
012    usedByTidepool = true
013)
014public class BolusRequestedMsg3HistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
015    
016    private int bolusId;
017    private int spare;
018    private float foodBolusSize;
019    private float correctionBolusSize;
020    private float totalBolusSize;
021    
022    public BolusRequestedMsg3HistoryLog() {}
023    
024    public BolusRequestedMsg3HistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int bolusId, int spare, float foodBolusSize, float correctionBolusSize, float totalBolusSize) {
025        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, bolusId, spare, foodBolusSize, correctionBolusSize, totalBolusSize);
026        this.pumpTimeSec = pumpTimeSec;
027        this.sequenceNum = sequenceNum;
028        this.bolusId = bolusId;
029        this.spare = spare;
030        this.foodBolusSize = foodBolusSize;
031        this.correctionBolusSize = correctionBolusSize;
032        this.totalBolusSize = totalBolusSize;
033    }
034
035    public BolusRequestedMsg3HistoryLog(int bolusId, int spare, float foodBolusSize, float correctionBolusSize, float totalBolusSize) {
036        this(0, 0, bolusId, spare, foodBolusSize, correctionBolusSize, totalBolusSize);
037    }
038
039    public int typeId() {
040        return 66;
041    }
042
043    /**
044     * <table border="1">
045     * <caption>Parsed fields for BolusRequestedMsg3HistoryLog:</caption>
046     * <tr><td><code>bolusId</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
047     * <tr><td><code>spare</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 12)</code></td></tr>
048     * <tr><td><code>foodBolusSize</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
049     * <tr><td><code>correctionBolusSize</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
050     * <tr><td><code>totalBolusSize</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 22)</code></td></tr>
051     * </table>
052     */
053    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
054        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
055        this.cargo = raw;
056        parseBase(raw);
057        this.bolusId = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
058        this.spare = Bytes.readShort(raw, 12);
059        this.foodBolusSize = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14);
060        this.correctionBolusSize = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18);
061        this.totalBolusSize = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 22);
062        
063    }
064
065    
066    /**
067     * <table border="1">
068     * <caption>Byte layout for BolusRequestedMsg3HistoryLog.buildCargo(...):</caption>
069     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>
070     * <tr><td>0</td><td><code>new byte[]{(byte) 66} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
071     * <tr><td>1</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
072     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
073     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
074     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
075     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
076     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
077     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
078     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
079     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
080     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
081     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
082     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(spare) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
083     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(spare) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
084     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>toFloat(foodBolusSize) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
085     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>toFloat(foodBolusSize) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
086     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>toFloat(foodBolusSize) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
087     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>toFloat(foodBolusSize) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
088     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>toFloat(correctionBolusSize) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
089     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>toFloat(correctionBolusSize) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
090     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>toFloat(correctionBolusSize) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
091     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>toFloat(correctionBolusSize) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
092     * <tr><td>22</td><td><code>toFloat(totalBolusSize) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
093     * <tr><td>23</td><td><code>toFloat(totalBolusSize) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
094     * <tr><td>24</td><td><code>toFloat(totalBolusSize) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
095     * <tr><td>25</td><td><code>toFloat(totalBolusSize) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
096     * </table>
097     */
098    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int bolusId, int spare, float foodBolusSize, float correctionBolusSize, float totalBolusSize) {
099        return Bytes.combine(
100            new byte[] { (byte) 66, 0},
101            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
102            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
103            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId), 
104            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(spare), 
105            Bytes.toFloat(foodBolusSize), 
106            Bytes.toFloat(correctionBolusSize), 
107            Bytes.toFloat(totalBolusSize));
108    }
109
110    /**
111     * @return bolus ID
112     */
113    public int getBolusId() {
114        return bolusId;
115    }
116    public int getSpare() {
117        return spare;
118    }
119
120    /**
121     * @return the portion of the bolus amount relating to food from carbs
122     */
123    public float getFoodBolusSize() {
124        return foodBolusSize;
125    }
126
127    /**
128     * @return the portion of the bolus amount relating to the correction bolus from BG+IOB
129     */
130    public float getCorrectionBolusSize() {
131        return correctionBolusSize;
132    }
133
134    /**
135     * @return the total bolus amount which is scheduled to be delivered following this message.
136     * note that this may not be correctionBolusSize+foodBolusSize if the amounts are overridden,
137     * or due to ieee float arithmetic
138     */
139    public float getTotalBolusSize() {
140        return totalBolusSize;
141    }
142}
